{"tid":1022783,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"隧道內被逼貼爬頭　嚇煞鐵騎　網民齊教點舉報","createTime":"2019-02-15T09:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T17:05:15.000Z","uid":225464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9a566ba4e850adda5178def4e527efe9848436e1","tid":1022783,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"<strong>隧道內被逼貼爬頭　嚇煞鐵騎　網民齊教點舉報</strong><br />\n<br />\n片LINK：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2RZTkB3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2RZTkB3&d=rje4l1xmTn6y9o%2BHBfPafwomF%2BlBZ%2FxAFwVMru4Rc7Q%3D&h=dbfdfa45\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2RZTkB3</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190215/photo/bkn-20190215164505625-0215_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190215170700\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190215%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190215164505625-0215_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190215170700&h=9af3ecec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咩事咁趕呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n深夜時分，多數人都想飛奔回家休息。惟近日有私家車在隧道內疑貪快爬頭，險與電單車相撞，情況驚險。<br />\n<br />\n片段被上傳至Facebook群組「馬路的事討論區」，可見星期五（15日）凌晨近3時，當時隧道右線亮起紅燈，禁止行駛。有私家車突然在右線駛至，逼近左線的電單車並越過雙白線爬頭。<br />\n<br />\n許多網民直斥私家車過分︰「呢啲司機一定要1823幫吓佢哋」、「師兄搞搞佢保障市民」、「呢啲X街唔使同佢客氣啦」。<br />\n<br />\n發貼者其後請教投訴程序，不少人熱心教學︰「燒隻碟，落口供」、「1823報時間地點人物」、「直接去案發現場就近的交通部報案室投訴」。"},{"pid":"36abb4b6a28bc240421aa3650a174811c4dee12d","tid":1022783,"uid":37458,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:12:49.000Z","msg":"成個故事呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定電單車搞鳩人先啦"},{"pid":"e6233236c5b69460ed4cd5d09e12d92175f07186","tid":1022783,"uid":18948,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"36abb4b6a28bc240421aa3650a174811c4dee12d","tid":1022783,"uid":37458,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:12:49.000Z","msg":"成個故事呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定電單車搞鳩人先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:16:06.000Z","msg":"無論電單車點樣搞鳩人佢都係犯法，有咩同個官講"},{"pid":"3320351583dd765a9b95e1459f283b7ca25a6adb","tid":1022783,"uid":998,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"36abb4b6a28bc240421aa3650a174811c4dee12d","tid":1022783,"uid":37458,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:12:49.000Z","msg":"成個故事呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定電單車搞鳩人先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:33:38.000Z","msg":"無論咩事, 揸車咁衝動都係對其他道路使用者構成危險, 危駕都鋤得入"},{"pid":"8760d834e6f068d523ab68120d19e9e3f1d9392b","tid":1022783,"uid":810,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"36abb4b6a28bc240421aa3650a174811c4dee12d","tid":1022783,"uid":37458,"like":2,"dislike":33,"score":-31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T00:12:49.000Z","msg":"成個故事呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定電單車搞鳩人先啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T08:39:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lih.kg/911857\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/911857</a><br />\n涉撞低鐵騎不顧被控危駕　男司機欲認不小心駕駛被拒"},{"pid":"66dff915347b60a2c2d49c3a6271493c449438e4","tid":1022783,"uid":41803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T15:01:29.000Z","msg":"貼白粉報link 唔該講明慎入"},{"pid":"94216e2fc41095369020eb74be3cfc9d2c255d16","tid":1022783,"uid":43520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"見過電單車隧道內爬頭, 逢車過車<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b73b16826236348808594e7098259aa9a922fcf","tid":1022783,"uid":182127,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T10:36:42.000Z","msg":"個隧道係咪叫迫迫Channel?"},{"pid":"47f9b7ff13b22f6cd63a06d1fc1227cbe852c64c","tid":1022783,"uid":35693,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"94216e2fc41095369020eb74be3cfc9d2c255d16","tid":1022783,"uid":43520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-21T09:57:56.000Z","msg":"見過電單車隧道內爬頭, 逢車過車<img src=\"/assets/faces/